Package me.dessie.dessielib.packeteer

Class Packeteer

java.lang.Object
me.dessie.dessielib.packeteer.Packeteer
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.bukkit.event.Listener
public class Packeteer extends Object implements org.bukkit.event.Listener
Event handlers for incoming and outgoing packets. Packeteer handlers should have a Packet and a Player as parameters.
